description: Another classmate of Alto, Michael and Luca, Matsuura is also Ranka Lee`s friend. A shy, quiet and voluptuous girl with glasses, she also works in the same "Nyan-Nyan" restaurant as Ranka and supports her dream of becoming a singer. Nanase is a skilled artist and was hired by Grace to become Ranka`s costume designer.
name: Matsuura Nanase
